prompt:
@female_runner emerges from shadow into neon-lit cyberpunk alley, rain streaming down her face, her leather jacket flaring behind her as she sprints. The camera handheld-tracks from behind, jostling with each footfall, rain droplets catching the neon glow in slow-motion bursts. She glances back over her shoulder — wide eyes, jaw clenched in desperate determination. Buildings blur past on either side, holographic billboards flickering. Her breath fogs in the cold air. one continuous shot, no cuts

Sound design (SFX only, no music): heavy rain patter on concrete, rapid footsteps echoing, her sharp intake of breath, distant police sirens wailing closer, neon buzz hum, fabric rustling from the sprint.

Style: cyberpunk noir, wet pavement reflections, neon pink and cyan lighting against dark brutalist architecture, 2.35:1 widescreen, 24fps, high-end cinematic production feel.
